Package: CoxianPhaseTypeR
Title: Fitting Coxian Phase-Type Distributions using EM Algorithm
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Dulan", "Dias", email = "ddias01@qub.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
)
Description: An R package for fitting Coxian Phase-Type distributions using the Expectation-Maximization (EM) algorithm based on the generalized formulas derived by Sheldon Ross. Supports parameter estimation, PDF evaluation, and survival probability computation for applications in survival analysis and other domains requiring phase-type distributions.
License: GPL-3
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    stats,
    Matrix,
    expm
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    roxygen2
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Encoding: UTF-8
